title: +1 to # of Tootie Mixes: Tootie's July 2015 Mix
description:
Another month, another Tootie mix. Nothing really special to mention this time around, although this mix ends with an unusually long stretch of Nu Metal. There are no intended deductive messages in this mix. Does my saying that make you think that there are?

*Infused audio portions utilized in this edit are lossily-sourced.

All tracks are sourced from lossless material unless noted. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
